+<p>On this page you setup the FRITZ!Box integrated answering machine.</p>
+<p>You can setup up to 5 answering machines and assign different settings to each answering machine.</p>
+<p><b>Selection of numbers for answering machine</b></p>
+<p>Select the numbers the answering machine should be used for. You can select up to 10 numbers.</p>
+<p><b>Activate answering machine</b></p>
+<p>Select this option if you want to turn on the internal answering machine.<br />
+Unselect this option to turn off the answering machine.</p>
+<p><b>Mode</b></p>
+<p>Select mode for answering machine:</p>
+<p>Select &quot;Mitteilungen aufnehmen&quot;, if you want to record messages.</p>
+<p>Select &quot;nur Ansage&quot;, if you don´t want to record messages.</p>
+<p><b>Telephone rings</b></p>
+<p>Select after which number of rings the answering machine should take the call.</p>
+<p>Select &quot;sofort annehmen&quot; to force the answering machine taking calls immediately.</p>
+<p><b>length of recording</b></p>
+<p>Select maximum length of each recording.</p>
+<p><b>PIN</b></p>
+<p>Select the PIN used to remotely enquire your answering machine. PIN must have 4 digits (0-9).</p>
+<p><b>PIN Confirmation</b></p>
+<p>Re-enter your PIN for confirmation.</p>
+<p>Click on &quot;Übernehmen&quot;, to save settings to FRITZ!Box.</p>
